TRANSCENDENT I: F.A.L.A.N.X. (The System) 

Role: Tactical Vanguard / Damage Siphon Tank Theme: The original military-grade "System" designed for absolute protection and area denial. 
Template: Component

1. THE PILOT: Commander Elias Vance 
Background: A veteran tactical lead chosen for his high cognitive sync rate with the FALANX core. 
Layered Defense Systems: Commander Vance manages a sophisticated multi-tier shielding array:
Inner Layer: Ancile Shield: The primary defense core. It can protect from all standard physical and energy threats but is vulnerable to specialized Plasma Attacks. 
Capacity: 100,000 HP. 
Outer Layer: Aegis Shield: An advanced energy barrier that can block any type of incoming damage without exception. 
Capacity: 60,000 HP. 

2. BASE FORM COMPONENTS & ABILITIES 
In his standard form, FALANX utilizes four modular components. Each features a signature "Active Ability." 

[COMPONENT: SWORD] Protocol Edge 
Description: A high-frequency blade designed for precision melee. 
Ability: TITAN SLASH: A brief startup charge followed by a massive, high-damage horizontal sweep. 

[COMPONENT: GUN] The Enforcer 
Description: A versatile mid-range ballistic rifle. 
Ability: LASER BEAM: The barrel overclocks to fire a continuous, concentrated beam of light. 

[COMPONENT: EXPLOSIVE] Calamity Shells 
Description: Shoulder-mounted ordinance launchers. 
Ability: CHIMERA: Launches 5 homing rockets in a burst. This can be repeated 5 times (total of 25 rockets). 

[COMPONENT: SHIELD] The Kinetic Siphon 
Description: A heavy physical shield that siphons 30% of damage taken by nearby allies to its own charge meter. 
Ability: SHATTER: The shield breaks into floating energy fragments called the AEGIS, providing 360-degree protection. 

3. SUPPORT SYSTEMS: THE SENTINEL DRONE 
Designation: SD-2 "Kestrel"
Ability 1: Missile Barrage: Automatically fires micro-missiles at nearby enemies every 1.5 seconds, dealing consistent chip damage. 
Ability 2: Emergency Reboot: Whenever any shield layer (Ancile or Aegis) drops to 0% HP, the drone instantly restores 15% of that shield's maximum health. 
Cooldown: 10 Minutes. 
Ability 3: Combat Link: Provides a permanent 5% damage boost to all of FALANX's weapon systems. 
Ability 4: Ghost Protocol: Every 15 minutes, the first hit taken by FALANX triggers an emergency cloaking field, making the unit invisible for 5 seconds to allow for repositioning. 

4. TITAN FORM (The Walking Exclusion Zone) 
When FALANX enters his Titan Form, his combat style shifts from a warrior to a strategic hazard. 
Titan Passive Customization: In Titan Form, FALANX can equip only 1 specialized passive module.

1) Titan Passive: Last Stand 
Effect: Immunity to ALL damage for 5s when HP drops to 5%. 

2) Titan Passive: Anticontrol 
Effect: Removes all debuffs when 3+ are active; grants temp immunity. 

3) Titan Passive: Antimatter Reactor 
Effect: Increases damage of all weapons by 10%. 

INTEGRATED COMPONENT: Titan Shielding 
Kinetic Siphon Integration: In Titan form, the Shield component is fused directly into the front-facing chassis. It continues to siphon damage from allies but gains a massive size increase. 
Ability: FORTRESS MODE: For 8 seconds, the siphon efficiency increases to 60%, and the Titan becomes rooted, creating an impassable physical barrier for enemies. 

PRIMARY WEAPON: Miasma Spreader 
Main Attack: Fires heavy-caliber Venomous Bullets with adaptive distance scaling. 
Close Range: Massive Impact Damage / Low Toxic Damage. 
Long Range: Lower Impact Damage / Massive Toxic Damage over time. 
Ability: GAS SPREAD: Unleashes a thick, toxic fog that slows enemies while granting FALANX thermal vision. 

PASSIVE SYSTEM: Solar Ignition 
Main Attack: Automatically deals fire damage every second to all enemies in a close-range radius around himself. 
Ability: SOLAR FLARE: Unleashes a massive 360-degree fire shockwave that applies a heavy Slow effect. 

5. STRATEGIC INTEGRATION: THE MOTHERSHIPS 
1) Mothership: Orion 
Callsign: The Sword 
Primary Orbital Protocol: Targeted Bombardment 
Effect: High-yield energy strikes that track enemy heat signatures. 

2) Mothership: Northlight 
Callsign: The Shield 
Primary Orbital Protocol: Restoration Beam 
Effect: Rapidly repairs FALANXâ€™s HP and cleanses all status debuffs. 

3) Mothership: Mute 
Callsign: The Silence 
Primary Orbital Protocol: System Lockdown 
Effect: For 20s, all enemy Actives and Passives are forcibly disabled. Also making them deal with 60% less damage. 

4) Mothership: Frederick 
Callsign: The Engine 
Primary Orbital Protocol: Aegis Pulse 
Effect: Grants massive speed and armor density boosts  and allies. 

6. MODULE COMPONENTS (Customization) 
Limit: 1 Active Module and 2 Passive Modules equipped at once (Standard Form). 

Active Modules (10-Second Duration) 

1) Module: Death Mark 
Effect: Target takes 50% increased damage from all sources. 

2) Module: Phase Shift 
Effect: Dimensional ghosting. Visible but immune to all damage.

3) Module: Advanced Repair 
Effect: Restores 20% of maximum HP over the duration. 

4) Module: Shield Breaker 
Effect: Disables enemy shields, leaving them fully vulnerable. 

5) Module: Quantum Radar 
Effect: Grants full visibility, including invisible/cloaked units. 

6) Module: Lockdown 
Effect: Attacks apply "Lockdown" status; targets cannot move when full. 

Passive Modules (Standard Form) 

1) Module: Last Stand 
Effect: Immunity to ALL damage for 5s when HP drops to 5%. 

2) Module: Overdrive Unit 
Effect: Deal +10% Damage when health is below 30%. 

3)Module: Accelerator 
Effect: Permanent 10% movement speed boost. 

4) Module: Heavy Armor Kit 
Effect: Increases FALANX's Max HP by 10%. 

5) Module: Anticontrol 
Effect: Removes all debuffs when 3+ are active; grants temp immunity. 

6) Module: Fortifier 
Effect: All Shield layers (Ancile/Aegis) gain +10% HP. 

